## Scope and boundaries

- This package targets **fullscreen fragment workflows** in Svelte, not general-purpose scene graphs.
- Main runtime works without the advanced entrypoint; advanced is for namespaced user state and extended type ergonomics.
- Documentation references behaviors currently implemented in this repository state, including test-verified edge cases.
